## 3. Variable Definitions

| Variable | Type | Values / Range | Description |
|----------|------|----------------|-------------|
| contest_id | string | 1-N | Unique identifier of primary contes |
| year | string | 1972-2012 | Primary contest year |
| party_id | integer | 1 = Democrat, 2 = Republican | Identifies contest party |
| party | string | DEM, REP | Party |
| endorsement_id | integer | 1-N | Unique identifier of endorsement event |
| endorser_name | string | First name + last name | Full name of endorser |
| endorser_first_name | string | First name | First name of endorser |
| endorser_last_name | string | Last name | Last name of endorser |
| endorser_id | integer | 1 - N | Unique identifier of endorser |
| endorser_description | Governor, U.S. Senator, U.S. Representative | Office/position of endorser |
| endorsee | string | Last name | Endorsed candidate |
| state | string | AK-WY | Endorser state |
| district | integrer | 1-N | Disctict of endorser (if representatitve) |
| region | string |      | Endorser region |
| home_state | integer | {0,1} | Indicates endorser and endorsee share the same home state |
| home_region | integer | {0,1} | Indicates endorser and endorsee from same home region |




